 Sammie, a former Big Brother Naija ‘Shine Ya Eye’ Housemate, has slammed a troll who body-shamed his father over a photo he shared on social media. He had posted a photo of his family celebrating Christmas on the microblogging platform Twitter. READ ALSO: Fans Offer Prayers To Sammie As He Reveals Struggle As he captioned the photo, the reality TV star wished his fans and followers a happy holiday season: Merry Xmas from me and the gang! The Jacobs, to be precise.
Sammie questioned the troll’s sanity after a toll body-shamed Sammie’s father, claiming that he is short and displeased with the statement. The troll wrote: Sam you papa short ooo He replied: Are you mad or something. 